---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="PIVOT Management Consultants | Break Lean Six Sigma Plateaus with TRIZ">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative bg-surface-alt border-b border-border">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 sm:py-16 lg:py-20">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <p class="font-heading italic text-ink-muted text-sm mb-2">Results — not reports.</p>
        <h1 class="text-[1.75rem] sm:text-[2rem] lg:text-[2.25rem] text-ink">
          When your Lean Six Sigma gains have plateaued, we break the constraint.
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm sm:text-base text-ink-light leading-relaxed">
          Operations consultants who use TRIZ to dissolve the trade-offs Lean Six Sigma can't — and transfer the capability so it lasts.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-5 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
          <a
            href="/diagnostic"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-2.5 bg-brand text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-brand-dark transition-colors"
          >
            Take the 4-min Breakthrough Diagnostic &rarr;
          </a>
          <a
            href="/results"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-2.5 border border-border text-ink text-sm font-medium rounded-lg hover:border-brand hover:text-brand transition-colors"
          >
            See client results &darr;
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Trust + clients in a compact row -->
      <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-border flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between gap-4">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-4 gap-y-1 text-xs text-ink-muted">
          <span>25+ years</span>
          <span>&middot;</span>
          <span>Published in Quality Digest</span>
          <span>&middot;</span>
          <span>Baldrige-level deployments</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-5 gap-y-1 text-xs font-medium text-ink-light">
          <span>Kaiser Permanente</span>
          <span>Northrop Grumman</span>
          <span>Syngenta</span>
          <span>Prudential</span>
          <span>Teledyne</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How it works -->
  <section class="py-12 sm:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-center mb-8">
        Lean reduces variation. TRIZ removes the trade-off.
      </h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-surface-alt rounded-lg p-5 border border-border">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
            <span class="w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-brand text-white text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center">1</span>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold">Identify the Wall</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-light">Your LSS program hit a trade-off it can't optimise away. Gains are flattening.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface-alt rounded-lg p-5 border border-border">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
            <span class="w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-brand text-white text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center">2</span>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold">Apply TRIZ</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-light">Structured innovation dissolves the contradiction — no compromise, no trade-off.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface-alt rounded-lg p-5 border border-border">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
            <span class="w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-brand text-white text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center">3</span>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold">Transfer the Capability</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-light">We embed until your team owns the method and the numbers move on your P&L.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Who we work with -->
  <section class="py-12 sm:py-16 bg-surface-alt border-y border-border">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-center mb-3">Who we work with</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-light text-center max-w-xl mx-auto mb-8">
        VPs and Directors of Operations, Quality, and Continuous Improvement whose improvement programs have plateaued — typically in manufacturing, aerospace, medical devices, and healthcare.
      </p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 text-center">
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-lg p-4 border border-border">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink">Operations</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-ink-muted mt-1">Throughput, cycle time, line redesign</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-lg p-4 border border-border">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink">Quality & ISO</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-ink-muted mt-1">9001, 13485, AS9100, CAPA</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-lg p-4 border border-border">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink">Innovation</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-ink-muted mt-1">TRIZ-driven product & process</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-lg p-4 border border-border">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink">Change</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-ink-muted mt-1">CI deployment, leadership alignment</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA band -->
  <section class="py-10 sm:py-14">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl mb-2">Not sure where your program stands?</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-light mb-5">The Breakthrough Diagnostic scores your organisation across 6 dimensions in 4 minutes.</p>
      <a
        href="/diagnostic"
        class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-2.5 bg-brand text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-brand-dark transition-colors"
      >
        Take the Diagnostic &rarr;
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
